      • put

        public DHTKey put(DHTKey key,
                  AbstractBufferedDHTObject vals)
        The put apply stores, according to a given key, a Value object in the distributed hash table. The apply also accept a array of values, so-called value partitions. These partitions are distributed over the nodes in the cluster. The key provides the complete metadata of all distributed partitions, the so-called partition directory.
        Parameters:
        key - The key that is associated with the value object.
        vals - A value object, or a array of value partitions.
        Returns:
        The key containing the distribution metadata of all value partitions.
